activities.message:
@yaworsk A fix for this was merged today and will be included in the next 8.12 patch release.

Please let me know how you'd like to be mentioned on the blog post and [vulnerability acknowledgements](https://about.gitlab.com/vulnerability-acknowledgements/), including your preferred name and an optional link.

Thanks again!

@yaworsk Thank you so much for bringing this up!

The fix was in the changelog at https://gitlab.com/gitlab-org/gitlab-ce/commit/9264816a34c45fb36c0117fe95bdf9e9af3287c8, but there was a communication breakdown and we failed to mention the issue and fix in the blog post. I just pushed https://gitlab.com/gitlab-com/www-gitlab-com/commit/7f77e70 to correct that.

Thank you again for your report and continued patience. Feel free to request a public disclosure.
